reviewText:
I kept waiting for DR. WHO to pop out of a telephone booth!

The mix of historical characters and time periods is baffling!

Please! If we are trying to make historical dramas of relevance to Christians, at least get writers who know how to stick to a proper  timeline.

This was returned.
  Wrong region, really would have loved it.
 Came on time, easy to open package great.
It give a better out look on the bible just what I was looking for thank you.
